results.title: IEC Standard Electric Motors , Flange Motors , Standard Motors
results.content: We manufacture standard 3-Phase Squirrel Cage Induction Motors, from IEC frames 63 to 160L are covered in the standard range and covers rating upto 15 Kw in 4 pole and corresponding standard ratings in different polarities. The standard range includes foot mounted (B3) versions as well as flange mounted (B5) and face mounted B14 versions. Special bigger size face mounting as per german (DIN) standards is also available. Technical details of all these are enlisted below. [...] Motors are in IEC frame sizes with fixing dimensions provided by IS 1231/IS 2223 for foot and flange mounted motors respectively.
